The second is a fragment (30.4 g, 7cm) of a wall sherd depicting a figure in an arcade. Possible second figure or ship in second arcade? Quality of mold was very poor, very little detail visible on figures. Figure on the right is in profile, facing left with an unidentifiable object in his/her hand.
